# Technical Requirements

## Backend Architecture
1. PHP Implementation
   - Single entry point (index.php)
   - Simple routing system
   - No frameworks

2. Database Structure
   - SQLite implementation
   - 5 core tables (users, family_groups, family_group_members, tasks, task_comments)
   - Prepared statements
   - Optimized for <100 users

## Frontend Implementation
1. JavaScript
   - jQuery for AJAX calls
   - DOM manipulation
   - Single app.js file
   - Minimal page reloads

2. CSS
   - Single style.css file
   - No frameworks
   - Mobile-first design
   - Responsive breakpoints